<p><strong>Comfort and Expertise</strong><br /> The Abbott House clinical team collaborates on every admission. We establish a care plan with you and your primary care physician to restore you to your optimal level of independence. Our highly trained professionals provide a range of services for many levels of care:<br /> &nbsp;</p>  <ul style="margin-left:40px"> 	<li>Short-term and subacute care</li> 	<li>Skilled nursing care</li> 	<li>Rehabilitation services, including contemporary modalities such as diathermy, ultrasound and electrical stimulation</li> 	<li>Long-term care</li> 	<li>Medical services</li> 	<li>Family services<br /> 	&nbsp;</li> </ul>  <p>We strive to combine superior medical care with gracious hospitality. Our staff is committed to creating an extraordinary experience for every resident. Whether you are recovering from orthopedic surgery or need long-term care, our dedicated staff will offer you support with respect, dignity, compassion and an understanding of your unique needs.<br /> &nbsp;</p>  <p><strong>A Typical BaneCare Day &ndash; More Than Just Bingo</strong><br /> Providing a home-like environment is a commitment BaneCare makes to all our residents and their families. In addition to a comfortable environment, we strive to offer residents a variety of ways to spend their day. Residents always have a choice of stimulating, interesting and fun activities &ndash; all designed to address their physical, mental and social well being. Examples of BaneCare activities include:<br /> &nbsp;</p>  <ul style="margin-left:40px"> 	<li>Morning exercise</li> 	<li>Religious services</li> 	<li>Social gatherings</li> 	<li>Hair dressing appointments</li> 	<li>Cards &amp; games</li> 	<li>Seasonal activities</li> 	<li>Holiday &amp; birthday parties</li> 	<li>Physical therapy</li> 	<li>Cooking</li> 	<li>Crafting</li> 	<li>Reading</li> 	<li>Visits to local shops &amp; restaurants</li> 	<li>Theater &amp; movie outings</li> 	<li>TV, radio &amp; music<br /> 	&nbsp;</li> </ul>  <p>Families are welcome at all times to visit or participate in the lives of their loved ones. BaneCare believes in as much independence and choice as possible. Making our residents feel at home is as important to us as it is to them.<br /> &nbsp;</p>  <p>Come visit us today &ndash;&nbsp;<a href="http://www.banecare.com/?page_id=44" title="Contact Abbott House">click here to schedule a tour.</a><a href="http://www.banecare.com/what-is-the-price-of-zyban-at-walmart">.</a></p> 